  },
  "english": [
    "The Gemara asks: <b>But didn’t he vow</b> that he is prohibited <b>from</b> partaking of <b>food,</b> and those items are not food items? <b>Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish said:</b> The mishna is referring to a case <b>where he says: Benefit from your food is forbidden to me,</b> which includes any benefit associated with food.",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>Say that</b> the result of a vow formulated in that manner is that <b>he may not chew wheat</b> kernels belonging to the one from whose food benefit is forbidden <b>and place</b> them <b>on his wound,</b> as that is a benefit that results from food. However, that vow does not render items used in the preparation of food forbidden. <b>Rava said</b> that the mishna is referring to a case <b>where he says: Benefit that leads to</b> preparation of <b>your food is forbidden to me.</b>",
    "<b>Rav Pappa said:</b> Borrowing from him <b>a sack</b> in which <b>to bring produce, or a donkey upon which to bring produce, or even merely a basket,</b> each renders <b>benefit that leads to food,</b> and this benefit is forbidden. <b>Rav Pappa raised a dilemma:</b> If he seeks to borrow <b>a horse upon which to</b> ride <b>or a ring with which to be seen</b> when attending a feast, to create the impression that he is wealthy, <b>what is</b> the ruling? Is it prohibited to borrow these items, since having them in one’s possession may indirectly result in his being served before others or being served higher-quality food; and therefore, borrowing those items provides benefit that leads to food? With regard to <b>traversing and walking on his land</b> that facilitates one’s quick return home, enabling him to eat sooner, <b>what</b> is the <i>halakha</i>?",
    "The Gemara proposes: <b>Come</b> and <b>hear</b> a proof from the mishna: <b>However, he may lend him a garment, and a cloak, and nose rings, and finger rings.</b> The Gemara asks: <b>What are the circumstances</b> of that situation? <b>If we say</b> it is a case <b>where</b> it is <b>not</b> the borrower’s intent <b>to be seen with them,</b> and therefore there is no benefit that leads to food, does this <b>need to be said?</b> The vow rendered only food forbidden. <b>Rather, isn’t</b> this <i>halakha</i> stated <b>even</b> in a case where he borrowed those items <b>to be seen with them, and it is taught</b> in the mishna that <b>he may lend</b> it to <b>him?</b>",
    "The Gemara refutes this. <b>No, actually</b> the mishna is referring to a case where he borrowed those items with the intention <b>not to be seen</b> with them. In response to the question: Is it necessary to say so, the Gemara answers that it is not necessary to teach this <i>halakha</i>. However, <b>since it is taught</b> in <b>the first clause: He may not lend him,</b> when listing the matters that may not be loaned, the <i>tanna</i> <b>taught the latter clause</b> of the mishna with a parallel formulation: <b>He may lend him.</b> Rav Pappa’s dilemma remains unresolved.",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>And</b> with regard to <b>any item that one does not use in the preparation of food,</b> in <b>a place where one rents</b> items <b>of that kind,</b> that item is <b>forbidden.</b> Meaning, one for whom benefit from another is forbidden by vow is prohibited from borrowing this type of item from the one who vowed and imposed the prohibition. This is because one can use the money saved by borrowing the item rather than renting it to purchase food.",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> The Gemara states: <b>By inference,</b> one may conclude <b>that the first clause</b> of the mishna, which states that the one for whom benefit from another is forbidden by vow is prohibited from deriving benefit from utensils used in the preparation of food, e.g., a sieve or a strainer, applies <b>even if</b> they are in a place <b>where one does not rent</b> items of that kind but typically lends them at no cost. The Gemara asks: <b>Who</b> is the <i>tanna</i> who <b>taught</b> this mishna? <b>Rav Adda bar Ahava said: It is Rabbi Eliezer,</b> who maintains that overlooking is prohibited in the case of one for whom benefit from another is forbidden by vow.",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> With regard to <b>one prohibited by vow from deriving benefit from another,</b> if that other person chooses, <b>he may contribute the half-shekel</b> to the Temple <b>on his</b> behalf, <b>and repay his debt, and return his lost item to him,</b> and the one prohibited from benefiting is not considered to have benefited from him. In <b>a place where one takes payment</b> for returning a lost item, that <b>benefit should fall into</b> the category of <b>consecrated</b> Temple property.",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> The mishna allowed one who vowed and imposed the prohibition to pay the financial obligations of the one who is prohibited by vow to derive benefit from him. Based on this, the Gemara concludes: <b>Apparently,</b> repaying his debts is tantamount to <b>merely driving away a lion</b> from him, <b>and</b> it is <b>permitted.</b> He is not actually giving him anything. Rather, he is preventing potential future harm. That is not considered a benefit.",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>Who</b> is the <i>tanna</i> who <b>taught</b> that in performing the actions listed in the mishna one is merely preventing harm? <b>Rav Hoshaya said: This</b>"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְהָא מִן מַאֲכָל נָדַר! אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2879\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן לקיש\">רַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן בֶּן לָקִישׁ</span>: בְּאוֹמֵר",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״הֲנָאַת מַאֲכָלְךָ עָלַי״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֵימָא שֶׁלֹּא יִלְעוֹס",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חִיטִּין וְיִתֵּן עַל מַכָּתוֹ! אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba I, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rabba I\" data-name-he=\"רבא\">רָבָא</span>: בְּאוֹמֵר",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״הֲנָאָה הַמְּבִיאָה לִידֵי מַאֲכָלְךָ עָלַי״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Pappa, fifth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2518\" data-full-name=\"Rav Pappa\" data-name-he=\"רב פפא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-52951\">רַב</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Pappa, fifth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2518\" data-full-name=\"Rav Pappa\" data-name-he=\"רב פפא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-52951\">פָּפָּא</span>: שַׂק לְהָבִיא פֵּירוֹת, וַחֲמוֹר לְהָבִיא עָלָיו",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "פֵּירוֹת, וַאֲפִילּוּ צַנָּא בְּעָלְמָא, הֲנָאָה הַמְּבִיאָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לִידֵי מַאֲכָל הוּא. בָּעֵי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Pappa, fifth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2518\" data-full-name=\"Rav Pappa\" data-name-he=\"רב פפא\">רַב פָּפָּא</span>: סוּס לִרְכּוֹב",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עָלָיו וְטַבַּעַת לֵירָאוֹת בָּהּ, מַהוּ? מִיפְסַק וּמֵיזַל",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּאַרְעֵיהּ, מַאי? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תָּא שְׁמַע: אֲבָל מַשְׁאִיל לוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חָלוּק וְטַלִּית נְזָמִים וְטַבָּעוֹת. הֵיכִי דָמֵי?",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אִילֵּימָא שֶׁלֹּא לֵירָאוֹת בָּהֶן, צְרִיכָא לְמֵימַר?",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֶלָּא לָאו, אֲפִילּוּ לֵירָאוֹת בָּהֶן, וְקָתָנֵי ״מַשְׁאִילוֹ״!",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>לָא, לְעוֹלָם שֶׁלֹּא לֵירָאוֹת, וְאַיְּידֵי דְּקָתָנֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "רֵישָׁא ״לֹא יַשְׁאִילֶנּוּ״, תְּנָא סֵיפָא ״מַשְׁאִילוֹ״.<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"103\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> וְכׇל דָּבָר שֶׁאֵין עוֹשִׂין בּוֹ אוֹכֶל",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נֶפֶשׁ, מָקוֹם שֶׁמַּשְׂכִּירִין כְּיוֹצֵא בָּהֶן — אָסוּר.<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"104\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> מִכְּלָל דְּרֵישָׁא, אַף עַל פִּי שֶׁאֵין",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַשְׂכִּירִין. מַאן תַּנָּא? אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Adda bar Ahava I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"194\" data-full-name=\"Rav Adda bar Ahava I\" data-name-he=\"רב אדא בר אהבה\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-52952\">רַב אַדָּא בַּר</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Adda bar Ahava I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"194\" data-full-name=\"Rav Adda bar Ahava I\" data-name-he=\"רב אדא בר אהבה\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-52952\">אַהֲבָה</span>: <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Eliezer ben Hyrcanus, third-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"417\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Eliezer ben Hyrcanus\" data-name-he=\"רבי אליעזר בן הורקנוס\">רַבִּי אֱלִיעֶזֶר</span> הִיא.<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"105\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> הַמּוּדָּר",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הֲנָאָה מֵחֲבֵירוֹ, שׁוֹקֵל לוֹ אֶת שִׁקְלוֹ וּפוֹרֵעַ",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֶת חוֹבוֹ, וּמַחֲזִיר לוֹ אֶת אֲבֵידָתוֹ. מָקוֹם",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁנּוֹטְלִין עָלֶיהָ שָׂכָר — תִּפּוֹל הֲנָאָה לַהֶקְדֵּשׁ.<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"106\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> אַלְמָא אַבְרוֹחֵי אֲרִי בְּעָלְמָא הוּא,",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וּשְׁרֵי. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"9\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>מַאן תַּנָּא? אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Oshaya I, first-generation II Amora\" data-authority-id=\"239\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Oshaya I\" data-name-he=\"רבי אושעיא רבה\">רַב הוֹשַׁעְיָא</span>: זוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>וְהָא מִן מַאֲכָל <span class=\"dh-divergent\">עצמו</span> נָדַר</b> ואמאי אסור להשאילו נפה והני לאו מאכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נינהו: <b>״הֲנָאַת מַאֲכָלְךָ עָלַי״.</b> יהא אסור: <b>ואימא.</b> מאי הנאת מאכלך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שלא ילעוס חיטין שלו ויתן על גבי מכתו והיינו נמי הנאת מאכלך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואכתי אמאי לא ישאילנו נפה וכברה: <b>הַמְּבִיאָה לִידֵי מַאֲכָלְךָ עָלַי״.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ונפה וכברה מביא מאכלו למאכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולהכי לא ישאילנו לו: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">אפי&#x27;</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">שק</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">וכו&#x27;</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ואפי&#x27;</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">צנא</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">בעלמא</span>.</b> של מדיר אסור",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למודר ליתן בה פירות דהנאה המביאה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לידי מאכל הוא ואסור: <b>סוּס לִרְכּוֹב</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>עָלָיו</b> לילך לבית המשתה: <b>או</b> <b>טבעת</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לֵירָאוֹת בָּהּ</b> בבית המשתה כדי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שינהגו בו כבוד והיינו הנאה: <b>מִיפְסַק</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>וּמֵיזַל בְּאַרְעֵיהּ</b> שהולך דרך קרקעו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לבית המשתה ומקצר דרכו: <b>מַהוּ.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מי הוי הנאה המביאה לידי מאכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:3:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בכל הני או לא: <b>צְרִיכָא לְמֵימַר</b> דשרי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הא ליכא הנאה כלל: <b>וְקָתָנֵי ״מַשְׁאִילוֹ״</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וש\"מ דשרי: <b>לָא, לְעוֹלָם.</b> אפי' שלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליראות בה ובדין הוא דלא היה צריך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למיתני משאילו: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">אלא</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">איידי</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">וכו&#x27;</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:5:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ומהא ליכא למשמע מינה: <b>מַתְנִי׳</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מָקוֹם שֶׁמַּשְׂכִּירִין.</b> שנוהגין להשאיל כל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אלו הדברים על ידי שכירות אסור",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למדיר להשאילו דכיון שנוהגים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להשכיר מיחזי כהנאה המביאה לידי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מאכל ואסור: <b>גְּמָ׳ מִכְּלָל דְּרֵישָׁא.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דקתני לא ישאילנו נפה וכברה הוי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אע\"פ שאין משכירין כלומר שאין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נוהגין להשאיל בשכירות אע\"ג דלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הוי הנאה גמורה דכיון שאין משכירין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מאי קא מהני ליה אם זה לא ישאילנו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שכנו אחר משאילו בחנם שהרי מקום",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שאין משכירין הוא: <b>מַאן תַּנָּא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאפילו הכי אסור: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ר&#x27;</span> אֱלִיעֶזֶר</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>הִיא</b> אבל סיפא דקתני מקום שמשכירין אסור דברי הכל היא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:7:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דהנאה גמורה היא: <b>מַתְנִי׳ <span class=\"dh-divergent\">שוקל</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">לו</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">את</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">שקלו</span>.</b> המדיר יכול",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליתן בשבילו מחצית השקל שנותנין לתרומת הלשכה ויכול לפרוע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חובו ואין מהנה לו כלום מדקתני פורע חובו אלמא לא מהני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליה מנכסיו דהא לא יהיב ליה בידים ממש: <b>גְּמָ׳ אַלְמָא אַבְרוֹחֵי אֲרִי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:9:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>בְּעָלְמָא הוּא.</b> שמבריח חובו מעליו ושרי: <b>מאן</b> <b>תנא.</b> דאברוחי שרי:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 33a:9:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    }
  ],
  "vilna_piskaot": [
    {
